	<a name="footnote13-22905_000_032">13.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.13?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 138:13</a>. My friend knew the suffering would help her prove herself (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.24-25?lang=eng#23" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 3:24&ndash;25</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.13-14?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 98:13&ndash;14</a>); learn to choose between good and evil (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.18?lang=eng#17" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">2 Ne. 2:18</a>); learn that blessings come after the trials (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.2-4?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 58:2&ndash;4</a>); learn obedience, patience, and faith (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/105.6?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 105:6</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/23.21?lang=eng#20" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Mosiah 23:21</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rom/5.3-5?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Rom. 5:3&ndash;5</a>); obtain a forgiveness of sin (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/hel/15.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Hel. 15:3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.50,60?lang=eng#49" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 132:50, 60</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 95:1</a>).</p>
